race.description: Tabtouch Regional Championship: Road To Ascot
race.comment: DREAMERS NEVER DIE (5) bolted in to score the Kalgoorlie heat last start as the race favourite, scoring by 3.9L in fine style. He now gets Pike in the saddle and comes into this on the fresh side. He races well on the fresh side and with the perfect draw, he looks the one to beat. BOLTA (1) won narrowly fresh but went to another level last start when winning by 1.7L in the Geraldton heat. He's likely to get back from the draw, but Galati is racing in top order and he's only third-up here. Ready to peak and looks the main danger. WINEACLOCKSUMWHERE (2) jumped a $1.35 chance last start and saluted with ease, bolting in by 5.2L. He has the speed to offset the wide barrier under Faithfull and he came into this campaign without a trial. Can continue his winning run. LEONARDO DA GREY (9) hasn't been far off BOLTA in his past couple, jumping favourite ahead of him last time out. Won't be far away again. VONSNIP (8) can improve third-up.
